---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Etiquette - Talia Sable" description="Booking etiquette and guidelines">
  <div class="hero">
    <img src="/header-business.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" class="hero-image" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="etiquette">
    <h1>Etiquette</h1>

    <div class="etiquette-content">
        <section class="etiquette-section">
          <h2>The Practicalities</h2>
          <p>I require a deposit for all appointments (50% for visits longer than 4 hours). Deposits are non-refundable and can be paid via giftcards, PayPal, or cryptocurrency.</p>
          <p>When we meet, tuck the rest in an unmarked envelope inside a book, or hand it to me discreetly if we're out.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="etiquette-section">
          <h2>If Plans Change</h2>
          <p>There's no penalty if you need to reschedule more than 48 hours before our date.</p>
          <p>Within 48 hours, I ask for 50% of the booking. Within 24 hours, 100%. Half can be applied to a rescheduled date within 4 weeks.</p>
          <p>If you're feeling ill, please tell me as soon as possible so we can reschedule.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="etiquette-section">
          <h2>Screening</h2>
          <p>I require either your real-world information (full name, phone, employment) or two provider references from the past year. This stays private and secure.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="etiquette-section">
          <h2>Boundaries</h2>
          <p>I reserve the right to say no if I'm not enjoying myself. The upside? If I'm doing something with you, you know it's because I want to.</p>
          <p>I'm best at playing myself. If you have a fantasy that requires me to be someone I'm not, I probably can't help. But roleplay as co-creation? That can be fun.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="etiquette-section gifts">
          <h2>Gifts</h2>
          <p>Never expected, always appreciated.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Gift cards:</strong> Article, Aman, Net-a-Porter</li>
            <li><strong>Treasures:</strong> Gold jewelry, ancient Greek and Roman coins, anything alpaca wool</li>
            <li><strong>My wishlist:</strong> <a href="https://www.luxylist.it/taliagracesable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The things I'm coveting right now</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
  </article>

  <div class="footer-image">
    <picture>
      <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/body-opera.jpg" />
      <img src="/header-royalton.jpg" alt="Talia Sable" />
    </picture>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  .etiquette {
    max-width: 990px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .etiquette h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .etiquette-content {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .etiquette-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .etiquette-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .etiquette-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .etiquette-section p {
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .etiquette-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .gifts {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .gifts ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .gifts li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .gifts strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .gifts a {
    color: var(--color-accent) !important;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .gifts a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover) !important;
  }

  .footer-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .footer-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      height: 50vh;
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .etiquette {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .etiquette-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
